subject:
New in Tome: More powerful AI page generation to help you shape your
 ideas.
content: Explore new directions for your ideas. Create a page ( https://tome.app/login?utm_campaign=Changelog+%239+-+Page+Generation%2B%2C+editor+UI+updates+-+07%2F13%2F2023+%28users%29&utm_content=Changelog+%239+-+Page+Generation%2B%2C+editor+UI+updates+-+07%2F13%2F2023&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io ) ( https://tome.app?utm_campaign=Changelog+%239+-+Page+Generation%2B%2C+editor+UI+updates+-+07%2F13%2F2023+%28users%29&utm_content=Changelog+%239+-+Page+Generation%2B%2C+editor+UI+updates+-+07%2F13%2F2023&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io ) Hi Shubhang, We‚Äôve designed Tome to help you explore all of the possibilities for bringing your ideas to life‚Äîno matter what shape or size they are. Keep reading for more on what‚Äôs new in Tome this week. Find the most compelling way to express your idea ( https://tome.app?utm_campaign=Changelog+%239+-+Page+Generation%2B%2C+editor+UI+updates+-+07%2F13%2F2023+%28users%29&utm_content=Changelog+%239+-+Page+Generation%2B%2C+editor+UI+updates+-+07%2F13%2F2023&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io ) Page generation just got more powerful, making it easier for you to shape and explore different realizations of your idea. Now you can quickly generate starting points for a 1-pager, landing page, blog post, or a page within a presentation. Now, when you type a prompt into the command bar, Tome will intelligently generate 4 different page variations‚Äîeach with a different approach to your topic, informational hierarchy, and design layout. You can hover over each option to see what it focuses on. Try it out by selecting the ‚ÄòCreate page about‚Ä¶‚Äô option from the command bar and entering one of these prompts: * Hidden gems to visit in California * PRD for a mobile app onboarding experience * Analyzing key themes from ‚ÄúMacbeth‚Äù * Significance of the Aurora Borealis * Resume for a product manager, highlight experience and education üí° Click here ( https://tome.app/blog/how-to-craft-prompts-for-page-generation?utm_campaign=Changelog+%239+-+Page+Generation%2B%2C+editor+UI+updates+-+07%2F13%2F2023+%28users%29&utm_content=Changelog+%239+-+Page+Generation%2B%2C+editor+UI+updates+-+07%2F13%2F2023&utm_medium=email_action&utm_source=customer.io ) to read tips from our team on page generation. Create more than just presentations We‚Äôve been so excited to see Tome creators share ideas with so many formats‚Äîfrom pitch decks and portfolios, to blog posts and 1-pagers. subject: Welcome to Presentations.AI
